.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, azure, orange
1. the person watching documentary movies is the fisherman##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the nurse is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes brown is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the coach##1
7. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Job           | nurse       | fisherman   | coach     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Color           | orange      | brown         | azure  |

