.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, teacher
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, salsa
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, february, january
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the teacher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person drinking tea is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the fan of reggae is the person drinking juice##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | juice         | tea     | coffee     |
| Job           | lawyer        | teacher | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | salsa   | dubstep    |
| Birthday         | january | september   | february |

