.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, potato, tomato
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, boat, trike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, water-polo
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | tomato     | potato    | avocado    |
| Transport         | airplane | trike | boat     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| Sport         | handball   | surfing   | water-polo |

 